<h2 class="left">UTOPIA OST - remastered for vinyl !</h2>

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<section class="blogs-content content-editor">
<h3>For those who were wondering: yes, we will release the OST to JAMAICA INN, we're just a little busy at this time of year, but it's coming! And Thanks for all the wonderful feedback!</h3>
<h3>UTOPIA season 1: ok, you ready? BIG VINYL RELEASE on its way, stay tuned!!</h3>
</section>

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<section class="blogs-content content-editor">
<h1><a href="https://serienoire.radio-canada.ca/accueil" target="_blank" rel="noopener">21h , Radio-Canada</a></h1>
</section>

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<section class="blogs-content content-editor">
<h2>Cristo has been nominated in the Original Score / Music category for the <a href="https://www.rts.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RTS Craft Awards </a>for his outstanding work on UTOPIA !!</h2>
<h2>The ceremony will take place in The Savoy Hotel, London, UK, on November 18th.</h2>
</section>

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

We'll be in L.A. between Oct 28th to Nov 2nd, to attend the Billboard Film &amp; TV conference - among other fun things.
Looking forward to meeting you there as well !

Get in touch with  <a href="mailto:kim@freerunartists.com">Kim Neundorf</a>  to talk about our upcoming projects and to get a special Hollywood tape that we prepared for you.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

SHOUT-OUT to Stephen Marsh at <a title="" href="https://www.marshmastering.com/">Marsh Mastering</a>, Los Angeles, Ca, for his phenomenal job !

Utopia OST release will be announced shortly - cheers!

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<a href="https://www.unippm.co.uk/#/en/news/Pre_Releases/a-future-darkly-pre-release.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">"A future darkly"</a> includes 7 of Cristo's tracks next to some amazing stuff by British composer <a href="https://raffertie.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Raffertie</a> !
Released on Atmosphere Music via <a href="https://www.unippm.co.uk/#/browse/browsed-results.aspx?selectedLabelId=1&amp;SelectedCDId=10160" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Universal Publishing</a> .
You can listen to it <a href="https://www.unippm.co.uk/#/browse/browsed-results.aspx?selectedLabelId=1&amp;SelectedCDId=10160" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

We just released a track on the <a href="https://www.apmmusic.com/bruton/the-story" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bruton Music Label</a> via <a href="https://www.unippm.co.uk/#/en/browse.aspx?selectedLabelId=27" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Universal Publishing</a> !
Bruton was owned by Michael Jackson between 1982-1985 - bummer !
<a href="https://www.unippm.co.uk/#/browse/browsed-results.aspx?selectedLabelId=27&amp;SelectedCDId=9834" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cristo on Bruton</a>

We are thrilled to announce the release of Cristo's pounding score for <a href="https://www.freerunartists.com/cristobal-tapia-de-veer/" target="_blank">The Girl with all the Gifts</a>. Vinyls are being pressed as we speak and should be out around February 24th, when the movie hits theatres in the US.

<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/ca/album/the-girl-with-all-the-gifts/id1194254284" target="_blank">Pre-order the album on iTunes</a>

All released by <a href="https://mondotees.com/collections/deathwaltz?page=1" target="_blank">Death Waltz Records / Mondo</a>.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

We are super happy to announce that finally, we were able to make schedules work to score one of our all time favourites!

More on that subject later this fall, stay tuned -

&nbsp;

Album will be released by our friends at LAKESHORE RECORDS. Get a taste here:

https://soundcloud.com/cristobal-tapia-de-veer/black-mirror-black-museum-original-score-music-sampler

&nbsp;

It was quite surreal to be honoured by a personal message from Isa on Cristo's work for Electric Dreams

and his Emmy nom, which closed with the words:

"... My dad would be so proud. ..."

Thank you so much Isa, this means the world to us - we always try to keep it (sur)real!

&nbsp;

